				<div class="nectar-fancy-box   hover_color_000000 icon_position_top disable-hover-movement " style="min-height: 300px" data-style="hover_desc" data-border-radius="5px" data-animation="" data-bg-animation="long_zoom" data-border="" data-delay="" data-alignment="center" data-color="accent-color" ><div class="box-bg" ></div><div class="inner"><i class="icon-default-style fa fa-wifi" data-color="accent-color" style="font-size: 50px!important; line-height: 50px!important;"></i><div class="heading-wrap">
<h2 style="text-align: center">Telecom</h2>
</div><div class="hover-content">At the heart of DeepSig’s signal processing are neural networks (NN) optimized specifically for telecom. Our software offers drop-in replacements within standard RAN components (e.g. O-RU, O-DU) to provide industry-leading performance that improves capacity, coverage, cost and energy efficiency.</div></div>  <a  href="https://www.deepsig.ai/omniphy-5g/" class="box-link"></a> </div>
			</div> 
		</div>
